快捷键
settings -> keymap -> eclipse
设置忽略大小写提示
settings -> editor -> general -> code completion -> match case (all letters)
设置文件创建的注释格式
settings -> editor -> file and code template -> includes -> File Header ->
/**
 * Copyright (c) ${YEAR}
 *
 * @author ${USER}
 * @date ${DATE} ${TIME}
 * @description
 */
开启ctrl + 滑轮调整字体大小
settings -> editor -> general -> mouse control -> change font size with CTRL + Mouse Wheel in
文件的编码格式设置为UTF-8
settings -> editor -> file encoding ->
自动导入、优化包
settings -> editor -> general -> auto import ->
多行显示标签页
settings -> editor -> general -> editor tabs -> multiple rows 或者 可以考虑把标签放在左侧展示也OK
idea 隐藏相关配置文件
settings -> editor -> file types -> ignored file and folders -> add *.impl
代码太长，超出字符换行
settings -> editor -> code styles -> hard wrap at 120 columns -> wrap on typing
设置方法的分割线
settings -> editor -> general -> appearance -> show method separators
配置git路径，一般来讲按照exe安装的已经会自动适配的
settings -> 搜索git即可
maven 配置
堆内存大小，以及build project auto
保存的时候自动格式化代码
settings -> tools -> action on save ->
配置项目级别代码格式化模板
保证开启：Settings → Editor → Code Style → Enable EditorConfig support ✔
直接创建.editorconf文件在项目跟目录

具体内容如下
````
# EditorConfig is awesome: https://EditorConfig.org
root = true


[*]
charset = utf-8
end_of_line = lf
insert_final_newline = true
trim_trailing_whitespace = true


# =============================
# Java（核心规则）
# =============================
[*.java]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 4
continuation_indent_size = 8
max_line_length = 120


# 空行与空白
trim_trailing_whitespace = true
insert_final_newline = true


# IntelliJ IDEA 专用扩展（识别但不影响其他编辑器）
# 大括号风格（K&R / Java 官方）
ij_java_brace_style = end_of_line


# if / for / while 后必须空格
ij_java_space_before_if_parentheses = true
ij_java_space_before_for_parentheses = true
ij_java_space_before_while_parentheses = true
ij_java_space_before_switch_parentheses = true
ij_java_space_before_catch_parentheses = true


# 运算符两侧空格
ij_java_space_around_assignment_operators = true
ij_java_space_around_logical_operators = true
ij_java_space_around_equality_operators = true
ij_java_space_around_relational_operators = true
ij_java_space_around_additive_operators = true
ij_java_space_around_multiplicative_operators = true


# 逗号
ij_java_space_after_comma = true
ij_java_space_before_comma = false


# import 规则（防止 *）
ij_java_class_count_to_use_import_on_demand = 99
ij_java_names_count_to_use_import_on_demand = 99


# 空行规则（对齐阿里规约）
ij_java_blank_lines_after_package = 1
ij_java_blank_lines_after_imports = 1
ij_java_blank_lines_around_class = 1
ij_java_blank_lines_around_method = 1


# 注解
ij_java_use_override_annotation = true


# =============================
# XML / YML / Properties
# =============================
[*.{xml,yml,yaml,properties}]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2


# =============================
# Markdown
# =============================
[*.md]
trim_trailing_whitespace = false
max_line_length = off


# =============================
# Shell / Script
# =============================
[*.sh]
indent_style = space
indent_size = 2

````


显示idea内存使用量
双击shift 输入 in memory indictor 单击即可在右下角看到内存占用


